data.description: Get ready to unleash your inner designer on this charming, end-unit, townhome that is waiting eagerly for its makeover! Sure, it needs a little sprucing up, but it has good bones and is begging for your DIY touches to make it your very own dream home. This kitchen is full of potential, with a dash of imagination and a sprinkle of magic, this space can be reimagined into a chef's dream. Will you go modern, how about farmhouse, or maybe traditional? Whatever you decide, just imagine whipping up some picture worthy meals. Get ready to host gatherings in your living & dining room. Or, snuggle up with a book in the cozy family room with a fire going inside the fireplace. Or, kick up your feet on your back patio and enjoy the low maintenance yard. Some of the hard work has been done: like the vinyl plank flooring through out the entire home (approx 2020), HVAC (replaced approx 2015), water heater (replaced approx 2020), and roof covering (approx 2017). Take your private tour today.
